    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera represents a purist\u2019s driving experience, powered by the M96 3.6L flat-six mated to a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal remains bone dry. The chassis features refreshed Bilstein dampers and poly-bushed control arms, ensuring the communicative steering and rear-biased weight distribution perform as Zuffenhausen intended. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor peppering on the nose, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system upgrades and a high-flow plenum\u2014are in excellent order for a spirited driver's car.",
